# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Shared .dockerignore for both Dockerfile.backend and Dockerfile.frontend.
# Build context is the repo root; this file trims build-irrelevant paths so
# `docker build` uploads less, caches better, and runs faster in GitLab CI.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Version control & IDE
.git/
.gitignore
.github/
.gitlab-ci.yml
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
*.user
*.suo

# .NET build artifacts (huge — never ship to the build context)
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/TestResults/
**/*.user
*.md
EVENTIY_ARCHITECTURE.md
README.md
ABOUT.md

# User secrets (NEVER bake into images)
**/secrets.json
**/appsettings.*.Development.json

# Angular build state & deps (npm ci will reinstall clean)
**/node_modules/
EventiyApp/dist/
EventiyApp/.angular/
EventiyApp/coverage/

# Local Docker / runtime artifacts
*.log
docker-compose*.yml

# Misc
obj/
Dockerfile.*
!.dockerignore
